userdoc.notice: Interface for the Meridian price oracle.*

params.DIAOracleAddress: The address of the master oracle to use
params.baseCurrency: the base currency used for the price quotes. If USD is used, base currency is 0x0
params.baseCurrencyUnit: the unit of the base currency
params.fallbackOracle: The address of the fallback oracle to use if the data of an aggregator is not consistent
params.priceAgeLimit: the max permitted age of oracle price before call is forwarded to fallback oracle

returns._0: address The addres of the fallback oracle
address The addres of the DIA oracle

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params.asset: The address of the asset to be set
params.key: The DIA keys/symbol of the source of each asset

params.AgeLimit: max age in seconds of latest price
